# Runtime SQLite mirror index (~200 MB, built by mirror:init). Never bundled —
# end users run mirror:init themselves. Excluded here so `mcpb pack` cannot bake
# the local .db into the .mcpb the way a root-only ignore pattern would miss.
/.mirror/
*.db
*.db-wal
*.db-shm
.env*
.mcpregistry_*
/.claude/
/.agents/
/skills/
/Dockerfile
/bun.lock
/bunfig.toml
/wrangler.toml
/biome.json
/tsconfig*.json
/vitest.config.ts
